<P>
<DATE>1976</DATE> -- <LOCATION>New Zealand</LOCATION>'s <PERSON>Brian Muldoon</PERSON> 
</P>
<P>
<DATE>1977</DATE> -- <LOCATION>Canada</LOCATION>'s <PERSON>Pierre Trudeau</PERSON> 
</P>
<P>
<DATE>1979</DATE> -- <PERSON>Fang Yi</PERSON>, Vice Premier of <LOCATION>China</LOCATION> 
</P>
<P>
